  <entry>
    <title>使用多个@RequestBody</title>
    <link href="/2021/07/13/mutil-requestbody/"/>
    <url>/2021/07/13/mutil-requestbody/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!--------------------------------- Title Start ---------------------------------><p><strong><font size=7 face="黑体"> </font></strong></p><!--------------------------------- Summary Start -------------------------------><p>如何在Controller中使用多个@RequestBody注解去获取body中的数据呢？</p><span id="more"></span><!--------------------------------- Content Start -------------------------------><h2 id="只能使用一个-RequestBody"><a href="#只能使用一个-RequestBody" class="headerlink" title="只能使用一个 @RequestBody"></a>只能使用一个 @RequestBody</h2><p>由于对HttpServletRequest 进行读取时，getInputStream()方法只能调用一次(认为body中的参数只需一次获取全部就能满足调用需求)，这样导致我们在接口中使用多个 @RequestBody 注解的话是会报错的。<front style="color: #7B68EE">IOException: Stream closed</front><br><img src="/img/mutil-requestbody/%E4%B8%8D%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AAbody.png" alt="alt 属性文本" title="不支持多个@RequestBody">  </p><p>如果不想要一个大对象获取所有的入参的话，可以使用 Map 的方式装载，想要什么参数就从map中get，但这种方式也不太优雅。下面的方法介绍通过代理模式修改getInputStream()方法，每次获取返回一个新的流，从而支持多个 @RequestBody 的使用。<br><img src="/img/mutil-requestbody/map%E6%8E%A5%E6%94%B6%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0.png" alt="alt 属性文本" title="map接收参数">  </p><h2 id="改进支持多个-RequestBody"><a href="#改进支持多个-RequestBody" class="headerlink" title="改进支持多个 @RequestBody"></a>改进支持多个 @RequestBody</h2><h3 id="ServletInputStreamCopier"><a href="#ServletInputStreamCopier" class="headerlink" title="ServletInputStreamCopier"></a>ServletInputStreamCopier</h3><p>自定义类继承 ServletInputStream，通过构造方法传入需要复制的byte[] 数组，这样每次返回自定义的对象都能获取到body中的内容。</p><details open><summary><strong> 代码 </strong></summary><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> org.apache.catalina.connector.InputBuffer;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> javax.servlet.ReadListener;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> javax.servlet.ServletInputStream;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> java.io.IOException;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> java.nio.ByteBuffer;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">ServletInputStreamCopier</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">extends</span> <span class="hljs-title">ServletInputStream</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">final</span> InputBuffer buf = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> InputBuffer();<br><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-title">ServletInputStreamCopier</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">byte</span>[] bodyCopier)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        buf.setByteBuffer(ByteBuffer.wrap(bodyCopier));<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">boolean</span> <span class="hljs-title">isFinished</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> buf.isFinished();<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">boolean</span> <span class="hljs-title">isReady</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> buf.isReady();<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">setReadListener</span><span class="hljs-params">(ReadListener readListener)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        buf.setReadListener(readListener);<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">read</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">throws</span> IOException </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> buf.read();<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></details><h3 id="RequestWrapper"><a href="#RequestWrapper" class="headerlink" title="RequestWrapper"></a>RequestWrapper</h3><p>注意到我们编写ReReadableHttpServletRequest时，是<front style="color: #7B68EE">从HttpServletRequestWrapper继承，</front><br>而不是直接实现HttpServletRequest接口,这是因为，Servlet的每个新版本都会对接口增加一些新方法。<br>从HttpServletRequestWrapper继承可以确保新方法被正确地覆写了，因为HttpServletRequestWrapper是由Servlet的jar包提供的，目的就是为了让我们方便地实现对HttpServletRequest接口的代理</p><details open><summary><strong>代码</strong></summary><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> org.apache.commons.io.IOUtils;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> javax.servlet.ServletInputStream;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequestWrapper;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> java.io.BufferedReader;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> java.io.IOException;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> java.io.InputStreamReader;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> java.io.UnsupportedEncodingException;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * 1、记录接口信息</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * 2、返回InputStream 支持多个<span class="hljs-doctag">@RequestBody</span></span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> */</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">RequestWrapper</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">extends</span> <span class="hljs-title">HttpServletRequestWrapper</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">byte</span>[] bodyCopier;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-title">RequestWrapper</span><span class="hljs-params">(HttpServletRequest request)</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">throws</span> IOException </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">super</span>(request);<br>        bodyCopier = IOUtils.toByteArray(request.getInputStream());<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     * 每次返回new ServletInputStream() 保证可重复获取流</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">     */</span><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> ServletInputStream <span class="hljs-title">getInputStream</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">throws</span> IOException </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.bodyCopier == <span class="hljs-keyword">null</span> ? <span class="hljs-keyword">null</span> : <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> ServletInputStreamCopier(bodyCopier);<br><br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-meta">@Override</span><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> BufferedReader <span class="hljs-title">getReader</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">throws</span> IOException </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> BufferedReader(<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> InputStreamReader(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.getInputStream()));<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> String <span class="hljs-title">getBody</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">throws</span> UnsupportedEncodingException </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.bodyCopier != <span class="hljs-keyword">null</span> ? <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> String(<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>.bodyCopier, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span>).replaceAll(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;\\n&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span>).replaceAll(<span class="hljs-string">&quot; &quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span>) : <span class="hljs-keyword">null</span>;<br>    &#125;<br><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></details><h3 id="在Filter中放入wrapper替代servletRequest"><a href="#在Filter中放入wrapper替代servletRequest" class="headerlink" title="在Filter中放入wrapper替代servletRequest"></a>在Filter中放入wrapper替代servletRequest</h3><p>最后在过滤器中放入我们修改后的RequestWrapper就行了</p><details open><summary><strong>代码</strong></summary><figure class="highlight pgsql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs pgsql"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> cn.dragon.framework.request.RequestWrapper;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> lombok.extern.slf4j.Slf4j;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> org.slf4j.Logger;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> org.slf4j.LoggerFactory;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> javax.servlet.*;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> java.io.IOException;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * @author lhl</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * @date 2021/4/29</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> * @desc 统计过滤器</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"> */</span><br>@Slf4j<br><span class="hljs-built_in">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> RequestLogFilter implements <span class="hljs-keyword">Filter</span> &#123;<br>    private static final Logger logger = LoggerFactory.getLogger(RequestLogFilter.<span class="hljs-keyword">class</span>);<br><br>    @Override<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">void</span> init(FilterConfig filterConfig) throws ServletException &#123;<br><br>    &#125;<br><br>    @Override<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">void</span> doFilter(ServletRequest servletRequest, ServletResponse servletResponse, FilterChain filterChain) throws IOException, ServletException &#123;<br>        Long start = <span class="hljs-keyword">System</span>.currentTimeMillis();<br>        HttpServletRequest request = (HttpServletRequest) servletRequest;<br>        RequestWrapper <span class="hljs-keyword">wrapper</span> = <span class="hljs-built_in">new</span> RequestWrapper(request);<br>        String uri = request.getRequestURI();<br>        logger.<span class="hljs-keyword">info</span>(&quot;接口：&#123;&#125;,入参：&#123;&#125;&quot;, uri, <span class="hljs-keyword">wrapper</span>.getBody());<br>        filterChain.doFilter(<span class="hljs-keyword">wrapper</span>, servletResponse);<br>        logger.<span class="hljs-keyword">info</span>(&quot;接口：&#123;&#125;,耗时：&#123;&#125;&quot;, uri, <span class="hljs-keyword">System</span>.currentTimeMillis() - <span class="hljs-keyword">start</span>);<br>    &#125;<br><br>    @Override<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">void</span> destroy() &#123;<br><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></details><h2 id="参考"><a href="#参考" class="headerlink" title="参考"></a>参考</h2><p><a href="https://www.liaoxuefeng.com/wiki/1252599548343744/1328976435871777">使用filter修改请求</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
